{"title":"最新指示响春雷","authors":["张金栋"],"dates":[{"year":1968,"month":10,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"最新指示响春雷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张金栋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最新指示响春雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"师傅心里战鼓催，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天还不亮就起床呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝着厂子走如飞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“徒弟选入革委会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千斤重担挑肩上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席咋说咱咋做，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可不能让他掉了队。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"找了半天没找到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽听车间机器声如雷："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“是谁来得这么早？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推门瞧，原来是徒弟小崔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“昨晚开会大半夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶快回家把觉睡！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老师傅假意扳脸把人训，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小徒弟激情话儿如潮水："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“永葆工人阶级本色，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心情你体会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两天没摸大锤把，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里憋得真不是味！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"徒弟话儿动心扉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"师傅激动得淌热泪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咚咚汽锤更欢畅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象在说：对，对，对……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}